testcase.title: To verify NumberOfSites Column is after RecruitmentStatus column in exportTrialResults

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "format = xls and query = cancer and offset = 0 and hits = 100 and expectedValues = exportDrugResults1.xls" as parameter to "exportDrugResults" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "exportDrugResults1.xls"
I should find "Last Update Date" column after "Other Actions" column in the exported file

check for all the columns "Drug Name,Originator Company,Active Companies,Active Indications,Target-based Actions,Highest Status,Technologies,Inactive Indications,Other Actions,Last Update Date" in the file

substeps.message: Number of records in the excel are equal to 100

steps.title: check results number is equal to the "100"
